********************To Install*************************************

To install, unzip and place 'RGBLEDHelper' folder into your 'C:\Users\{user name}\Documents\Arduino\libraries' folder or '{Arduino IDE path}\hardware\libraries" or {Arduino IDE path}\libraries" directory. 

Restart the Arduino IDE, look for the Library under "Sketch" -> "Import Library".

All uses of the library are in the example sketchs. 


